  <brief_title>Co-infections in Children Hospitalised for Bronchiolitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Co-infections in Children Hospitalised for Bronchiolitis: Incidence, Clinical Symptoms and Influence of Cohort Isolation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
